{"tid":2262704,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"子瑜又被欺負？新宣傳照「臉大一倍」照樣釋出粉絲怒：攝影師出來面對","createTime":"2020-10-29T10:01:55.000Z","updateTime":"2020-10-29T11:48:30.000Z","uid":74065,"like":0,"dislike":6,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"812da2af97ccd7f0e857e8ae183580d2ed48bbe1","tid":2262704,"uid":74065,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-29T10:01:55.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.ltn.com.tw/Upload/style/page/2020/10/28/201028-14843-1-dNvxG.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.ltn.com.tw%2FUpload%2Fstyle%2Fpage%2F2020%2F10%2F28%2F201028-14843-1-dNvxG.jpg&h=be07134e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n子瑜新宣傳照「臉大一倍」照樣釋出，讓粉絲不滿。（翻攝自official.twice、queentzuyu IG，以下同）<br />\n<br />\n韓國女團 TWICE 近期強勢回歸，隨著宣傳照一波接一波，也讓女孩們聲勢持續飆漲！不過在新釋出的宣傳照中，台灣成員周子瑜卻有幾張照片被發現不只拍照角度不ok、小臉更是直接放大一倍成大餅臉，惹得粉絲質疑難道釋出前都不把關的嗎？怒喊攝影師出來面對！<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.ltn.com.tw/Upload/style/page/2020/10/28/201028-14843-2-sAWXA.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.ltn.com.tw%2FUpload%2Fstyle%2Fpage%2F2020%2F10%2F28%2F201028-14843-2-sAWXA.jpg&h=cd1f25ea&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\nTWICE 近期強勢回歸，話題也不斷。<br />\n<br />\n子瑜長相甜美又是隊中的老么，一直以來備受關注，不過卻總是被發現「差別待遇」。像是拍攝團體照時，她經常都站在角落，還被封為「Corner Queen」；要不然就是得屈膝、或站不直好配合其他人身高，都讓粉絲替她委屈。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.ltn.com.tw/Upload/style/page/2020/10/28/201028-14843-4-rcV5K.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.ltn.com.tw%2FUpload%2Fstyle%2Fpage%2F2020%2F10%2F28%2F201028-14843-4-rcV5K.jpg&h=a3a60520&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n子瑜因身高最高，大合照時經常站在角落。<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.ltn.com.tw/Upload/style/page/2020/10/28/201028-14843-7-hTqIJ.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.ltn.com.tw%2FUpload%2Fstyle%2Fpage%2F2020%2F10%2F28%2F201028-14843-7-hTqIJ.jpg&h=4f05530f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\nTWICE出新專輯，子瑜為了配合大家還站歪的，被網友無奈指出是「喪屍站法」。<br />\n<br />\n這回新照釋出，子瑜穿著黃色格子洋裝搭小外套，還戴上珍珠項鍊呈現小女人風，不過不只笑容顯得有點不自然，臉龐線條更是完全消失、直接變成大餅臉腫一倍，讓粉絲直呼不敢相信狂砲轟！<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.ltn.com.tw/Upload/style/page/2020/10/28/201028-14843-5-pltYS.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.ltn.com.tw%2FUpload%2Fstyle%2Fpage%2F2020%2F10%2F28%2F201028-14843-5-pltYS.jpg&h=1fcb05cc&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n子瑜這波新宣傳照臉龐顯得浮腫，讓網友怒轟攝影師濫用顏值隨便拍！<br />\n<br />\n粉絲質疑：「子瑜臉怎麼好腫」、「攝影師把子瑜的臉拍的超大！不可以濫用顏值好嗎」、「攝影師不知道有沒有考慮要轉行」、「欺負我們顏值高就可以不修圖嗎」？<br />\n<br />\n還有不少網友認為，因子瑜是隊中最高，平時拍團體照要她站角落或配合身高就算了，但這回獨照搞成這樣也太令人不可思議，質疑就算攝影拍不好、難道經紀公司釋出前都不把關的嗎？「是否變相欺負」、「經紀公司也要負責吧」等話題也在韓國社群引起熱議。<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.ltn.com.tw/Upload/style/page/2020/10/28/201028-14843-6-lQF0S.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.ltn.com.tw%2FUpload%2Fstyle%2Fpage%2F2020%2F10%2F28%2F201028-14843-6-lQF0S.jpg&h=1580e38b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n團體照經常站角落的子瑜，也被封為「Corner Queen」。<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.ltn.com.tw/Upload/style/page/2020/10/28/201028-14843-8-BbkRG.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.ltn.com.tw%2FUpload%2Fstyle%2Fpage%2F2020%2F10%2F28%2F201028-14843-8-BbkRG.jpg&h=ae548d63&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n網友認為經紀公司也要負責任，可惜了子瑜的高顏值。"},{"pid":"3e1e959c8d395094c88a11a7e67ae047c08d78b6","tid":2262704,"uid":256952,"like":1,"dislike":3,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-29T10:02:58.000Z","msg":"高顏值。<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/28.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/28.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/28.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a74cda5a6ecd122f00062dd9b39cb212da5d9880","tid":2262704,"uid":320858,"like":4,"dislike":2,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-29T10:04:04.000Z","msg":"不嬲下巴短 面圓 ，而家先知<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"79e2836656e6fad98ee2bc07589946538de21e6a","tid":2262704,"uid":2781,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-29T10:15:50.000Z","msg":"欺負我們顏值高就可以不修圖嗎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"476b48f4790d